### Additional Notes Re: Wordshoal
\begin{itemize}
\item Intuitive -- Scales well with uncertainty \par \vspace{2.5mm}
\item Capable of diagnosing both $\theta_i$ but $\beta_j$ across documents (debates) \par \vspace{2.5mm}
\item Missingness = Random Error 
\end{itemize}

